      "description": "Presenting a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen boasts a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed as preventative maintenance. The chassis remains rigid, retaining original suspension geometry with no bushing deflection. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains a factory-depth luster with zero orange peel or clear coat failure. A true driver\u2019s car preserved in an uncompromising state of mechanical perfection.",
