    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman is a pristine example of precision engineering, maintained to a standard that rivals its first day on the showroom floor. The Jet Black Metallic paint retains a deep, mirror-like clarity, free of the common road rash, swirl marks, or stone chips typically found on performance vehicles. It has been treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating and has resided exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of untouched leather and brushed aluminum; the bolsters on the sport seats are firm and show no signs of compression or wear, and the interior still carries that distinct factory aroma. Every electronic component, from the crisp infotainment display to the tactile response of the steering wheel controls, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is impeccable, with a documented service history performed strictly by certified technicians. With low mileage and zero modifications, this vehicle offers the rare chance to own a modern masterpiece in absolute 'wrapper' condition. The sale includes two original keys, all owner\u2019s manuals, and a bespoke indoor car cover.",
